        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/888/600/medium/9d2dbe36-4250-4497-bcc6-daf746ec9557.png" srcset="" alt="View Course" height="419" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FDE62100-1F04-0135-A9C9-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>View the new course. Depending on your institution's preference, you can use either the <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-Course-Setup-Checklist/ta-p/1139" target="_blank">Course Setup Checklist</a> or the <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-Canvas-course-setup-tutorial-as-an-instructor/ta-p/1013" target="_blank">Canvas Course Setup Tutorial</a> to populate your course.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
